  "title": "What Did I Just Kill?",
  "description": "displays a small toast with information about the mob you just killed",
  "body": "<h1>What Did I Just Kill?</h1>\n<h4>displays a small toast with information about the mob you just killed</h4>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/nRZZ43X/divider-dark-green.png\" alt=\"divider\" width=\"1903\" height=\"10\" /></p>\n\nthe information displayed in the toast can be changed through the config  \nfor more information see the wiki\n<a title=\"Wiki\" href=\"https://github.com/tristankechlo/WhatDidIJustKill/wiki\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/nRZZ43X/divider-dark-green.png\" alt=\"divider\" width=\"1903\" height=\"10\" /></p>\n\n<h3>Example Images</h3>\n\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/1MXM1y4/entity-normal.png\" alt=\"entity-normal\" border=\"0\">\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/W59MNM3/entity-one-line.png\" alt=\"entity-one-line\" border=\"0\">\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/rHcdCxR/entity-one-line-no-distance.png\" alt=\"entity\" border=\"0\">\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/zrnmvrr/entity-normal-named.png\" alt=\"entity-normal-named\" border=\"0\">\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/CMPx6N0/player-normal.png\" alt=\"player-normal\" border=\"0\">\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/nRZZ43X/divider-dark-green.png\" alt=\"divider\" width=\"1903\" height=\"10\" /></p>\n\nYou are a mod developer and want to add support for your entities?\n<br/>\nHave a look at this <a title=\"Guide\" href=\"https://github.com/tristankechlo/WhatDidIJustKill/wiki/Modded-Entities\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Guide</a>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/nRZZ43X/divider-dark-green.png\" alt=\"divider\" width=\"1903\" height=\"10\" /></p>\n\nif you have any questions about the mod, or you want a few insights about upcoming features:\n<br>\nfeel free to join the &nbsp;&nbsp;\n<a title=\"discord\" href=\"https://discord.gg/bhUaWhq\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/VQ66pHN/Discord.png\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"166\" height=\"32\" />\n</a>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;\n<a title=\"discord\" href=\"https://discord.gg/bhUaWhq\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">link</a>\n",
